725165f-b.title: Queens: 27th Street - Ditmars Boulevard
725165f-b.text:
27th Street, west side, north from near Ditmars Boulevard,
showing the grounds of the Seacrest Sanitarium, formely the River
Crest Sanitarium. View 2 is in the opposite direction (north)
from near 21st Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  May 27, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2:
